I-wonder
========

An awful (http://wiki.call-cc.org/egg/awful) application example.


How to see it in action
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Clone this repository then:

  $ cd i-wonder
  $ chicken-install
  $ csi -s create-db.scm wonderings.db sql/captchas.sql
  $ awful example-app.scm

Then just point your browser to http://localhost:8080
